Instalacion:

Python:
	- viene por defecto instalado
	- python3 --version
	
C++:
	- sudo apt-get update
	- sudo apt-get upgrade
	- sudo apt-get install g++
	
Cmake:
	- sudo apt-get install cmake
	- cmake --version
	
Git:
	- sudo apt-get install git
	- git --version
	
Minicom:
	- sudo apt-get install minicom
	- Configuracion 
		-> minicom -s
			-> Configuracion del puerto serial 
				-> Dispositivo Serie: /dev/ttyACM0

Raspberry Pi Pico SDK:
	- Clonar el repositorio (https://github.com/raspberrypi/pico-sdk.git)
	- Install CMake and GCC cross compiler
		- sudo apt install cmake gcc-arm-none-eabi libnewlib-arm-none-eabi libstdc++-arm-none-eabi-newlib
	- Configurar los paths -> nano ~/.bashrc
		export PICO_SDK_PATH=/home/davidaqc/pico/pico-sdk

